    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[阅读论文：Three-view generation based on a single front view image for car]]></title>
        <id>https://04lm40.github.io/post/yue-du-lun-wen-three-view-generation-based-on-a-single-front-view-image-for-car/</id>
        <link href="https://04lm40.github.io/post/yue-du-lun-wen-three-view-generation-based-on-a-single-front-view-image-for-car/">
        </link>
        <updated>2021-03-29T02:44:27.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>多视角，2020<br>
<strong>问题</strong>:输入图像没有包含足够的像素信息时，生成的图像质量不佳。<br>
<strong>流程</strong>：粗粒度视图生成（信息约束网络）---&gt;细粒度视图生成<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1616988547379.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>信息约束网络</strong>：三个端到端生成网络（编解码网络）：左视角生成，顶视角生成，前视角生成。相互约束。<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617005022811.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>损失函数</strong>：L1和感知损失<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617005162226.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>改进视角生成</strong>：<br>
<strong>大像素块表征</strong>：在缩放过程中，使用最近邻插值对粗糙视图进行缩放，使粗糙视图中的一些模糊像素与其他像素合并成一个大像素块。128×128--&gt;16×16--&gt;128×128(每行16个大像素块)<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617008324687.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>细化网络</strong>：pix2pix，判别器最后一层改全连接层，LS loss。<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617008781306.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>损失函数</strong>：系数：100，0.06<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617009202064.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>大像素块迁移</strong>：我们将一些大像素块从训练集迁移到测试集，以提高视觉效果。SSIM用于从训练集中找到最接近大像素块视图A的大像素块视图B，然后根据颜色差异将合格的大像素块从B迁移到A。<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617009598712.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>数据集</strong>：ShapeNet中的车类。<br>
<strong>对比方法</strong>：L1，AFN,TVSN,TBN<br>
<strong>合成点云外壳</strong>：我们找到了三视图的最小包彩色图像<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>C</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C_{i}(i=0,1,2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.07153em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>和相应的二进制图像<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>B</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B_{i}(i=0,1,2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.05017em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，并使用它们来构建一个点云壳。<br>
<img src="https://04lm40.github.io//post-images/1617010441557.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
]]></content>
